	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require a small piece of quartz.</p><p><strong>[[/save dexterity]]{Dexterity Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 10d6 cold]] damage and is moved to one side of the wall of your choice.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, and the creature moves to the nearest unoccupied space of their choice.</p></li><li><p><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area covered by the wall is &amp;reference[obscuredheavily].</p></li><li><p>It has AC 12, 30 hit points, and all its ability scores are 0, except &amp;reference[constitution]{constitution} which is 16. The wall is to vulnerable to &amp;reference[fire]{fire} damage. It is also immune to all conditions except cover and &amp;reference[obscured]{obscured}.</p></li><li><p>Reducing a 10-foot section of wall to 0 hit points destroys it and leaves behind a sheet of frigid air in the space the wall occupied. A creature moving through the sheet of frigid air for the first time on a turn must make a Constitution saving throw.</p><p><strong>[[/save constitution]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 5d6 cold]] damage and is moved to one side of the wall of your choice.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, and the creature moves to the nearest unoccupied space of their choice.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage from the wall appearing by [[/damage 2d6 cold]]{2d6} and damage from passing through the wall by [[/damage 1d6 cold]]{1d6} for each spell level above 6th.</p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
